      "para_id": "Q000884.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , Ur-Bau , ruler of Lagaš , the child born to Ninagala , made an eternal thing appear : he built and restored his E-ninnu-anzud-babbar ."
    }
